(Scratch that last Diamond post. He posted before I did.)

Diamond::
She heard the blasts hit the pod. She cursed under her breath. Che 
checked the scanners. It was a maximal firing on her. "How could a 
Maximal get this close to the Allience base and live?"

She opened her link. "ZARDUS!! I'm under attack. Kill this Maximal 
for me so I can land without crashing."
She went into evasive manouvers and aimed the pod to the base. She 
activated the emergency trhusters and excelerated the pods decent 
towards the Allience base.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, RoboRick007 <rfa007@h...> wrote:
> ::DrillBit::
> 
> He heard KitKat. He ran to the room in a panic. He found her.
> "Oh my god!" He picked her up, and took her to a CR.
> "Hold on. Dont die on me!"
> He put her in and set it for toxins and vireses. He monetered her
> recovery.
> 
> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> Hot Rod saw a pod go by with Diamond. He reconized her.
> "Hot Rod, MAXIMIZE!"
> He transformed, and fired a rocket at it.
> "Now where are you going in such a hurry?"
> 
> ::Demolition::
> 
> With Angel Prime gone, he went to the CR's and started repairing.
